Additional information about submission: These experiments were conducted as part of the release of the GEO-Bench-V2 datasets. The results differ from the main experimenst in that they use SAR input bands (vv and vh) for backbones with those bands. Additionally, the best performance is selected between between multi-modal (Sentinel1 + Sentinel2) results and Sentinel2 only results.
